{"tid":1023693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰以色列飛港客機　起落架陷跑道爛地","createTime":"2019-02-16T03:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T10:43:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53fe794d0b895ded717e3da3b083eaca13df2301","tid":1023693,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜排名節節下跌、洩漏940萬客戶個人資料的國泰航空</span></ins></strong>，一班日前由以色列特拉維夫飛香港的客機在推出停機坪時，左側主起落架陷入水泥路中逾5小時，機上乘客需改乘其他航班。現時未知事故成因，但有傳媒指是因機坪日久失修。<br />\n<br />\n社交網Facebook群組The TLV Spotters於周五（15日）晚發文，指涉事的是航班編號CX676、全新的A350客機，移動時起落架的輪胎陷在水泥中，國泰其後要求所有乘客下機，並安排他們乘搭其他航班。據報職員設法讓飛機脫困，但沒有對策，飛機入夜後仍未被推走。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，一架新的A350無法執飛長達數小時，會對航空公司造成重大損失，因為它需要安置乘客、再安排他們乘搭其他航班等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190216/bkn-20190216100042540-0216_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190216%2Fbkn-20190216100042540-0216_00822_001.html&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=b5f90b2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190216/bkn-20190216100042540-0216_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e93a7f800c367b2b22ba46fc014022f78641e570","tid":1023693,"uid":6063,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"以色列機場出問題講到好似因航錯咁"},{"pid":"3c2058d3d3eb314b252a1bba364f0cd812d3e9dd","tid":1023693,"uid":36287,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"關因航撚事"},{"pid":"dde193a4dfeff4cc99a5deefb0bd8c49d84066b0","tid":1023693,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2058d3d3eb314b252a1bba364f0cd812d3e9dd","tid":1023693,"uid":36287,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"關因航撚事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"已經變左一個名稱呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p